==Useful Info==
'''Golden eyes''' are fast, constantly-blinking pack enemies that do no damage, but try to [[confusion|confuse]] you with their gaze if they can overcome your [[willpower]]. They can be found in [[the Slime Pits]], [[Abyss]], and can be summoned by a few enemies through the [[Summon Eyeballs]] spell.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Having at least Will+++ or [[clarity]] will render them harmless.
*[[Wand of iceblast|Wands of iceblast]] and [[Fireball]] are excellent for bypassing their annoying [[EV]] at range, but mind the [[noise]].
*[[Airstrike]] will usually one-shot them, given their low HP, lack of AC, and flight.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.18]], golden eyes couldn't [[see invisible]].
*Prior to [[0.16]], they were immune to magic.
